# Summary
This documentation page explains how to create a local evaluation flag in Amplitude Experiment, including steps for creating a new flag with local evaluation mode and migrating an existing remote evaluation flag to local evaluation, with specific instructions on changing evaluation mode settings and updating bucketing keys.

